      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"judicial activism\"? That sounds pretty loaded. Are you saying the current majority is basically just making up new laws instead of actually following the Constitution? I thought the whole point of Originalism was to stay true to the text, so why are you calling it a \"partisan shift\"?",
