      "content": "That's a strong take. But what about the other side? If I'm writing this paper, I need to understand why some legal scholars say the Court is actually being faithful to the text. Isn't there a legitimate argument that the \"militia\" clause doesn't limit the right of the individual? How would someone defending the current ruling describe their logic?",
